    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Example of injection using DLT"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Precondition: Connect DLT with proper COM port number setting"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We can automate this precondition. Work in progress"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "When you connect DLT make sure the ECU ID is SCC. Other wise injection will not work"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/5.%20Injecting%20Command%20using%20DLT/image-2023-4-19_11-27-43.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/5. Injecting Command using DLT/image-2023-4-19_11-27-43.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "DLT Injection: Send Command as shown in below picture"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "For command format refer this page 4. Test Command format - XC-CT China - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below is the example from Zeekr project"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/5.%20Injecting%20Command%20using%20DLT/image-2023-3-25_17-26-23.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/5. Injecting Command using DLT/image-2023-3-25_17-26-23.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Test Case: After this command is executed our Test case API will be called command data"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "panel_type": "info",
      "title": "Input Data Processing",
      "content": "inputData_a will have complete input data. Inside test case we need extract Test case input data which starts from Seventh byte"
    },
